title: Run to End Endo: 5k
description: Join The Endo Network's Run to End Endo 5k in Vancouver to raise awareness and funds for endometriosis support, research, and education. This event welcomes all ages and abilities, with participants running or walking to support the cause.

venue.name: Stanley Park
venue.description: Stanley Park is a 1,001-acre public park in Vancouver, featuring beautiful trails, beaches, and views of the city skyline and mountains.
